    • Method Detail

      • hash

        long hash(T x)

        Computes a hash which is not unique but returns for an object x the same value.

        If two objects are the 'same' will be determined by the Object.hashCode() and Object.equals(Object) methods.

        Parameters:
        x - the object for which the hash shall be computed
        Returns:
        the hash for the object
